### List assets
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/assets?page=1&limit=25&asset_class=Stock&search=world
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Get asset by ISIN
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/assets/IE00BK5BQT80
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Create asset
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/assets
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isin": "IE00BK5BQT80",
  "name": "Vanguard FTSE All-World UCITS ETF",
  "asset_class": "Stock",
  "currency": "EUR",
  "exchange": "Milan"
}

### Update asset
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/v1/assets/IE00BK5BQT80
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Vanguard FTSE All-World UCITS ETF USD",
  "asset_class": "Stock",
  "currency": "EUR",
  "exchange": "Milan",
  "yahoo_ticker": "VWCE.MI"
}

### Refresh asset price from Yahoo Finance
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/assets/IE00BK5BQT80/refresh-price
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Store manual asset price
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/v1/assets/IE00BK5BQT80/price
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "2026-04-18",
  "close_price": "123.45000000",
  "currency": "EUR"
}

### List asset price history
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/assets/IE00BK5BQT80/price-history?page=1&limit=25&from_date=2026-01-01&to_date=2026-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
